=============================
Task 008 Word Count in Scala
=============================
This assignment is to do task 4 in scala:
    read shakespeare file
    count each word
    return the word and it's count
    Store in csv file, with header word and count 

=============================
Files and Directories
=============================
WordCount.scala      scala code to perform word count task
wordcount_scala.csv  results of the code
run.sh               script to execute the scala code
README               this file

=============================
Getting Started
=============================
To execute this task, execute the run.sh script as follows:
cd to the 008-WordCountInScala directory:
    ./run.sh

=============================
Prerequisites
=============================
The following tools will need to be installed to complete this task:
    Java 8
    Scala 2.11.8

=============================
Installing
=============================
No special installation process is required for this task. Ensure the 
prerequisites are installed and execute the run.sh script.

=============================
Results
=============================
Upon completion, the wordcount_scala.csv should exist and have this format:
	word,count
	ophel,2
	damne,1
	sounding,1
	diseases,1
	follow,21
	sundaies,1
	demand,2
	queene,39
	beetles,1
	sister,8
	vnproportion,1
	begge,6
	former,2
	tutor,1
	labour,2
	pleasant,1
	pickhaxe,1
	gentlemen,12

